TextBody:
Hello,

Does this happen on windows?
Can you please check if "Advanced Printer and MTP Scanning:" is enabled in the global settings?
If it is can you please:
- disable it,
- Update the policies on the Epp client,
- restart the computer
- test if the issue is present.

Kind regards
__________________
Andrei Pop | Technical Support Engineer
Netwrix Endpoint Protector
